    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Sept 20 article on Rev Reginald T Jackson: number of black and Hispanic men shot and wounded by police during Apr 1998 traffic stop on New Jersey Turnpike was three, not four</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article yesterday about the Rev. Reginald T. Jackson, director of the Black Ministers Council in New Jersey, which has campaigned against racial profiling by the state police, misstated the number of black and Hispanic men shot and wounded by state troopers during a traffic stop on the New Jersey Turnpike in April 1998. It was three, not four.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
